WEBVTT

00:00:57.360 --> 00:01:02.416
that their horrific brutality
and violence are true jihad,

00:01:02.440 --> 00:01:06.616
I want to say that their idea
of jihad is wrong --

00:01:06.640 --> 00:01:07.976
completely wrong --

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:09.200
as was mine, then.

00:01:11.200 --> 00:01:13.560
Jihad means to strive to one's utmost.

00:01:14.440 --> 00:01:17.456
It includes exertion and spirituality,

00:01:17.480 --> 00:01:18.976
self-purification

00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:20.200
and devotion.

00:01:22.480 --> 00:01:25.256
It refers to positive transformation

00:01:25.280 --> 00:01:29.376
through learning, wisdom
and remembrance of God.

00:01:29.400 --> 00:01:32.640
The word jihad stands
for all those meanings as a whole.